	<h1 class="title">黑马逆袭：世界杯上7个亮了的小众赞助商</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/11/small/11.jpg?1399473966" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">吴亭蓉</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2014-06-23 10:05:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/1216/medium/1216.jpg?1436639435" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


